OL,3,CMurder victim's brother recieves PSNI
OL,4,Capology over failings
OL,6,FA terminally ill man has welcomed the
OL,7,Fpersonal delivery of an apology by the
OL,8,FChief Constable over police failings
OL,9,Ffollowing the murder of his brother.
OL,11,FEugene Thompson's brother Paul was
OL,12,Fmurdered in 1994 by loyalist
OL,13,Fterrorists.
OL,15,FThe 25-year-old died after being shot
OL,16,Fwhile in a taxi in the area of
OL,17,FSpringfield Park on his way home.
