OL,6,FEarlier that evening, UDA terrorists
OL,7,Fare believed to have cut a hole in a
OL,8,Fpeace line fence to access the area
OL,9,Fwhich was reported to police.
OL,11,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher delivered
OL,12,Fan apology to Mr Thompson in hospital
OL,13,Fin Belfast on Tuesday which
OL,14,Facknowledges failures by police.
