OL,6,FIt describes Paul Thompson's murder as
OL,7,F"tragic and senseless", and pays
OL,8,Ftribute to his brother and mother
OL,9,FMargaret, who has since died, for
OL,10,F"great courage and resilience in their
OL,11,Fjourney for the truth about his
OL,12,Fmurder".
