OL,6,FIt also acknowledges the original
OL,7,Fpolice investigation did not identify
OL,8,For pursue all lines of inquiry and
OL,9,Fsignificant disclosure delays at the
OL,10,Finquest.
OL,12,F"The police service apologises
OL,13,Funreservedly to Eugene for the above
OL,14,Ffailings on the part of policing which
OL,15,Fimpacted adversely both on the
OL,16,Fdelivery of justice for Paul and on
OL,17,Fhis family's quest for the truth," it
OL,18,Fsaid.
