OL,6,F"We are committed to improving how we
OL,7,Fhelp families and communities impacted
OL,8,Fby the troubles by being more open,
OL,9,Ftransparent and victim-focused, and by
OL,10,Fdisclosing as much information as we
OL,11,Fpossibly can.
OL,13,F"The police service believes that
OL,14,Ffurther information about Paul's
OL,15,Fmurder can safely be released to
OL,16,FEugene and hopes that the pending
OL,17,FSupreme Court judgment will allow for
OL,18,Fthis to happen."
