OL,4,Capology over failings
OL,6,F"I thanked Jon Boutcher for coming
OL,7,Fhimself and for acting quickly in
OL,8,Fdelivering the apology from the PSNI
OL,9,Fafter we had asked for it," he said.
OL,11,F"That's different to the British
OL,12,FSupreme Court, who also know my
OL,13,Fsituation, and I had hoped they would
OL,14,Fhave made their judgment by now, but
OL,15,Fthere is no sign of it.
OL,17,F"The apology makes clear the RUC
OL,18,Fdidn't investigate and arrest suspects
OL,19,Fwhen they could have and that they
OL,20,Fcould have done things that could have
OL,21,Fprevented Paul's murder."
