OL,6,FDaniel Holder, director of the
OL,7,FCommittee on the Administration of
OL,8,FJustice (CAJ), said Mr Thompson and
OL,9,Fhis mother "long fought for justice
OL,10,Fand truth in relation to Paul's
OL,11,Fmurder".
OL,13,FHe added: "The High Court and Court of
OL,14,FAppeal ruled over a year ago that
OL,15,FEugene was entitled to see the
OL,16,Finformation in the coroner's 'gist'.
OL,18,F"The Secretary of State appealed the
OL,19,FSupreme Court hearing was back at the
OL,20,Fbeginning of June and Eugene is still
OL,21,Fawaiting the ruling.
