OL,12,FConstable, Jon Boutcher, held a
OL,13,Fprivate meeting with Mr Eugene
OL,14,FThompson, the brother of Liam Paul
OL,15,FThompson, during which he provided a
OL,16,Fstatement of apology on behalf of the
OL,17,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland for
OL,18,Ffailings identified on the part of the
OL,19,FRUC and PSNI."
